sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    actor Receptionist
    participant Backend
    participant DB
    actor TV
    actor Mobile

    Note over Receptionist,TV: Register New Patient

    Receptionist->>Backend: POST /api/patients
    Backend->>DB: Insert patient and queue
    DB-->>Backend: Token created
    Backend->>Backend: Calculate wait time
    Backend-->>TV: queue_updated
    Backend-->>Receptionist: queue_updated
    Backend-->>Mobile: queue_updated
    Backend-->>Receptionist: HTTP 201

    Note over Receptionist,TV: Call Next Patient

    Receptionist->>Backend: POST /api/queue/call-next
    Backend->>DB: Update queue status
    DB-->>Backend: Success
    Backend->>Backend: Recalculate wait time
    Backend-->>TV: patient_called
    Backend-->>TV: queue_updated
    Backend-->>Receptionist: queue_updated
    Backend-->>Mobile: queue_updated
    Backend-->>Receptionist: HTTP 200

    Note over Receptionist,TV: Complete Consultation

    Receptionist->>Backend: POST /api/queue/complete
    Backend->>DB: Save consultation
    DB-->>Backend: Success
    Backend->>Backend: Update analytics
    Backend-->>Receptionist: queue_updated
    Backend-->>TV: queue_updated
    Backend-->>Mobile: queue_updated